p: Using the time-series data of the number of laboratory-confirmed IBV cases per lineage and specific humidity, we estimated the parameters ( α, a, b, and κ) in the model described in the last section. Based on previous study [ 21] we parameterized ε as 1/ ε = 0.6 day and γ as 1/ γ = 4.0 day. These parameters are estimated for each lineage. We also estimated the herd immunity against each lineage at the beginning of the period explored in this study, i.e., SS, SR, RS, RR at the beginning of the 2010–2011 season. Hereafter, we refer to SS, SR, RS, RR at the beginning of the 2010–2011 season as SS(0), SR(0), RS(0), RR(0), respectively.
